"""Hardcoded commune list per French department.

Generated 2026-05-04 from SIRENE database (one-time).
Source: companies table, GROUP BY (departement, ville), excluding MAPS entities.
Filtered to valid French dept codes only (drops bad SIRENE rows with sentinel dept values).
Sorted by SIRENE-registered company count descending per dept.

Total: 41258 (departement, ville) combinations across 106 departments.
Format: {dept_code: [(ville_name, sirene_company_count), ...]}

NOT a runtime SIRENE query — file is static and committed to the repo.
To regenerate (rare, e.g., after annual INSEE commune merger): re-run the SIRENE
GROUP BY query and overwrite this file.
"""

